{
  "stem": "1917.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 67.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they told him that the had a tiny little ulcer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we cleared that problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think that all the trauma-- that he was in concentration camp four years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He actually grew up in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The problem that I find with him, that he's not willing to face his problems.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He's trying always to run away from them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Well the fact is, you cannot run away from your problems.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You cannot run away from yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You have got to face your problems head on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he has not learned that yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all my good will that I brought with me, I became extremely depressed after the second child was born.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by the time she was two years old and my son was four, I wanted to commit suicide-- because I wanted a family, and that was not a family.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What really happened was I was driving around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I filed for divorce papers, because I said, I didn't want to live that way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had a nervous breakdown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mind would go-- I would lose half a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wouldn't know where- I was with children in the car, and I didn't know what happened, and where they were, and why I was there, and how long I was there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it really scared me to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- because I didn't know how I was going to support them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I felt that the least I owed my children was the security of a roof over their head, and food in their mouth, and somebody to care for them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I knew that I couldn't go ahead with the divorce.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked very hard at it myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My husband never lifted a finger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to see a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
